Package: grizbayr
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Inference for A|B and Bandit Marketing Tests
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Ryan Angi
Maintainer: Ryan Angi <rangi@redventures.com>
Description: Uses simple Bayesian conjugate prior update rules to calculate 
    the following metrics for various marketing objectives:
      1. Win Probability of each option
      2. Value Remaining in the Test
      3. Percent Lift Over the Baseline
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
